	SYNTAX

What is SYNTAX
==============

SYNTAX allows to generate parsers based on their grammatical
descriptions. Recognized formalisms: CFG (deterministic or ambiguous),
TAG, LFG, RCG, ...


Installation
============

See the INSTALL file for the compilation and installation procedure.


Documentation
=============

More information can be found on SYNTAX home page:

<http://syntax.gforge.inria.fr/>


Availability
============

You can visit SYNTAX GForge project page to browse the Subversion
repository, download releases or submit a bug...

<http://gforge.inria.fr/projects/syntax/>


